{
  "stem": "19969.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was on the far, extreme corner of the whole post-- occupied only a small portion of the entire garrison area.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just a, a small-- well, it was a confinement area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Maybe it was a mile all the way around-- a-- around the thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But it was a fairly substantial area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then I could see-- when I first got to where I could see it, I was right next to a place that I found was a crematorium.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I looked in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they had bodies stacked in a small, cement room next to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "These were nude bodies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And were stacked like cordwood in that building-- in that little, small building.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And next to it was a crematorium that had four, four coal-fired furnaces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The furnaces were not operating when we got there, and I don't think had been operating for several days because they were cold.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I surveyed that for a minute or two.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I went out to follow the path along the wall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The-- I saw the confinement was a-- it was a high, barbed-wire fence surrounding the area.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was a guard tower about every 200 yards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there was huge cement guard towers with a machine gun and a small, German crew at each guard tower.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Well, I came across the first guard tower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And there were five German soldiers lying near the base of the tower, which I immediately assumed had been the crew that was in that guard tower.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, I assumed that my men had killed them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Then I walked on down-- one of the-- one of the I Company men said, Colonel, the entrance to this is right down here.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
